Mauritius’s Tourism Bookings Lag Behind 2010, l’Express Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-09-19T05:39:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/mauritius-s-tourism-bookings-lag-behind-2010-l-express-says.html
Mauritius’s tourism bookings for
the beginning of the high season are below those for 2010,
l’Express reported, citing Jocelyn Kwok, chief executive officer
designate of the Association des Hoteliers et des Restaurateurs
de l’Ile Maurice.  There is no improvement in bookings for the September to
November period, the Port Louis-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis via Johannesburg at 
1933 or  gbell16@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
